# Network Standard (Tier-1 Baseline)

## Purpose:  
This document defines the standardized network architecture and enforcement model for all HaaS deployments.

This baseline ensures:
- DNS control and visibility
- VLAN isolation
- Prevention of DNS bypass
- Consistent, repeatable deployments

